Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.90,0:00:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\bord0\fad(1500,500)\pos(190,170)}第一夜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.90,0:00:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs20\bord0\fad(1500,500)}编剧：史蒂文·莫法特
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.70,0:00:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这裙子可有点大胆啊\N{\fs14}The dress is a little daring.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.15,0:00:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 所以我换了这件\N{\fs14}Yep, so I went for this instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.17,0:00:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要出去玩吗\N{\fs14}Are we going out?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.00,0:00:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,家长大人们都在睡觉\N{\fs14}Parents are asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.40,0:00:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,风暴监狱住的如何啊\N{\fs14}How's Storm Cage?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.49,0:00:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚可是我那12000年终身监禁的第一夜啊\N{\fs14}I'm on the first night of 12,000 consecutive life sentences.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.28,0:00:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,目前还不好说 我们去哪儿\N{\fs14}Kind of early to say. Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.49,0:00:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,卡德伦贝塔星\N{\fs14}Alderin Beta.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.03,0:00:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,挺无聊的 到处都是油炸食品店\N{\fs14}Boring, planet of the chip shops.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.31,0:00:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 那里有棵高达122米的大树\N{\fs14}But there is a 400-foot tree growing out of a clifftop
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.10,0:00:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,长在海中央的大山的北门的悬崖边上\N{\fs14}on the north side of a mountain in the middle of the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.41,0:00:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你乘坐TARDIS上到顶端\N{\fs14}And if you take the lift to the top and look up,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.67,0:01:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,在2360年9月21日凌晨过12分的时刻\N{\fs14}at exactly 12 minutes past midnight on the 21 st of September, 2360,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.97,0:01:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你就会看到全宇宙史上最多的星星\N{\fs14}you can see more stars in one sky that at any other moment in the history of the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.05,0:01:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,亮如白昼 非常神奇\N{\fs14}It's like daylight, only magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.96,0:01:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你都能借着星光读书了\N{\fs14}You could read a book by it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.64,0:01:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我不读书的话也没关系吧\N{\fs14}Whoo! Is it okay if I don't?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.50,0:01:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,还剩10分钟 快去换衣服\N{\fs14}We've got 10 minutes. Get dressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.82,0:01:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这句话差一点就完美了\N{\fs14}Oh, that's so close to the perfect sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.12,0:01:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你带日记本了吗\N{\fs14}Did you bring the diary?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.44,0:01:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这是日记本?\N{\fs14}It's a diary?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.20,0:01:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,现在是了 因为 River\N{\fs14}It is now, because River,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.18,0:01:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,从现在开始 我们要定下规矩\N{\fs14}from now on, there are rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.88,0:01:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,喔 你变得好严格啊 我倒也不介意\N{\fs14}Ooh, you've gone all strict. Not that I mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.64,0:01:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,River 我们两个的顺序完全错乱了\N{\fs14}River, you and I, it's all in the wrong order.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.34,0:01:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我们从不按正常顺序相遇\N{\fs14}We never meet in sequence.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.61,0:01:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你要把所有事都写入日记中\N{\fs14}You put everything in the diary
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.69,0:01:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,才好确认我们走到哪一步了\N{\fs14}so we know where we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.68,0:01:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我能写什么 亲爱的\N{\fs14}Put what in the diary? Sweetie,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.90,0:01:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我可是被关在宇宙最高安保等级监狱里呢\N{\fs14}I'm in the highest security prison in all of the known universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.28,0:01:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,据说 River Song 能在那个监狱来去自如\N{\fs14}River Song could walk in and out of the prison like the walls aren't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.08,0:01:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是 River Song\N{\fs14}I'm River Song.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.82,0:01:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那不就行了\N{\fs14}Then you'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.55,0:01:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你不喜欢这条裙子 衣柜里还多得是\N{\fs14}If you don't like the dress, there's plenty more in the wardrobe.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.37,0:01:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,右转再左转 就在那堆乱七八糟的后面\N{\fs14}First right, second left, just past the helter-skelter.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.36,0:01:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,River\N{\fs14}River!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.97,0:01:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我就知道你会回来的\N{\fs14}I knew you'd come back here,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.20,0:01:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你这个怀旧的傻瓜\N{\fs14}you nostalgic idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.61,0:01:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,抱紧我\N{\fs14}Hold me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.28,0:02:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,River\N{\fs14}River!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.53,0:02:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,River\N{\fs14}River!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.48,0:02:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,River\N{\fs14}River?
